### On setting up .editorconfig for Vscode
* Install editor config plugin from editorconfig.org
* Right click on the project and generate editorconfig
* Ctrl + P Prerences : Open workspace settings - Format on paste
* Ctrl + P Prerences : Open workspace settings - Format on save
* Ctrl + P Prerences : Open workspace settings - Detect Indentation
* Do npm install -g editorconfig
